dsDescriptionValue.value: The dataset contains output from an ensemble of CESM1(WACCM) simulations of the 1783-1784 Laki eruption in Iceland. We have submitted two manuscripts to the Journal of Geophysical Research: Atmospheres based on analysis of the output of these simulations. There are ~3000 files, totaling ~17GB of data. The data include all output analyzed in the two manuscripts: temperature, zonal and meridional wind, sea level pressure, precipitation, cloud fraction, aerosol effective radius, SO4 concentration, SO2 concentration, radiation, aerosol optical depth, sea surface temperature, cloud droplet/ice number concentration, soil moisture, average water/ice number concentration, EP flux and its divergence, meridional residual circulation streamfunction

publicationCitation.value: Submitted to JGR: Atmospheres. Will update when published.
